@startuml
title Viaverse Subscription / Sponsored Placement — State Diagram

[*] --> TRIALING
TRIALING --> ACTIVE : trial ends / paid
ACTIVE --> PAST_DUE : charge failed
PAST_DUE --> GRACE_PERIOD : dunning
GRACE_PERIOD --> ACTIVE : payment recovered
GRACE_PERIOD --> LIMITED : grace expired
LIMITED --> ACTIVE : paid
ACTIVE --> CANCELLED : cancel

[*] --> AD_DRAFT
AD_DRAFT --> AD_REVIEW : submit
AD_REVIEW --> AD_LIVE : approved + budget
AD_LIVE --> AD_PAUSED : budget cap/manual
AD_PAUSED --> AD_LIVE : resume
AD_LIVE --> AD_ENDED : budget/date ended

CANCELLED --> [*]
AD_ENDED --> [*]

note bottom
Subscription state gates business features; ad state gates sponsored visibility.
Ad approval never overrides business suspension or search safety/relevance gates.
end note
@enduml
